text: The Nissan Terrano II was a automobile that was made by Nissan, introduced in 1993. It was replaced by the Nissan Qashqai in 2006. == Engines == * 2.4 85 kW (116 hp), 87 kW (118 hp) and 91 kW (124 hp) * 2.7 TD 74 kW (100 hp) and 92 kW (125 hp) * 3.0 Di 113 kW (154 hp) ==Other websites== Terrano II Category:1990s automobiles Category:2000s automobiles
title: Nissan Terrano II
